                  <h3 className="text-xl font-semibold">Map / Spider Network Placeholder</h3>
                  <p className="text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mt-2">
                    Connect Leaflet or MapLibre here to render Hyderabad Metro corridors, city bus routes, interchange hubs, stop clusters, and spider-style connectivity.
                  </p>
                  <div className="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center">
                    <Badge className="rounded-xl">stops.txt</Badge>
                    <Badge className="rounded-xl">routes.txt</Badge>
                    <Badge className="rounded-xl">trips.txt</Badge>
                    <Badge className="rounded-xl">stop_times.txt</Badge>
                    <Badge variant="secondary" className="rounded-xl">shapes.txt optional</Badge>
                  </div>
